Class CompositeResponseAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.protocol.client.http.CompositeResponseAccessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpResponseAccessor

    public class CompositeResponseAccessor
extends java.lang.Object
implements HttpResponseAccessor
    Composite HttpResponseAccessor.

    Composes several instances HttpResponseAccessor instances and provides access to the HTTP response for each of them.

    Per HttpResponseAccessor.access(HttpResponse) none of the instances is supposed to throw a RuntimeException. In case some of them do, the rest of the composed instances will not be provided with the HTTP response.
